data.name: BlackTube | Dark Theme
data.description:
This theme only works on the old youtube layout, so follow the instructions below

step 1: download this zip and unzip - https://dropmefiles.com/CRRTX
step 2: open your browser and click on the extension option
step 3: click on the option to load an extension and select the previously extracted folder

Please leave your feedback
If you find bugs please report me

data.name: spotify.com mini player
data.description: I've modified the Spotify web player at open.spotify.com to enable for a more compact view. It does not interfere with the work area when listening while working. If you set the blowser window width to less than 960px, you will get a compact view. It is optimized for display at a width of about 340px.
